short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension displays the color palette codes for the Google logo.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension simply displays the hex, RGB, and CYMK color palette details for the Google logo and the Purple used in Google Forms. This can be handy for designers of any level of expertise.
long.es: This extension simply displays the hex, RGB, and HSL color palette details for the Google logo. This can be handy for designers of any level of expertise. November, 2017 - Added the Deep Purple for Google Forms and the Google Grey.
